<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3530] Do not start LogSyncer when not in deferred flush mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3530</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently we always start the LogSyncer thread, even when not necessary because the &quot;deferred flush&quot; is set to false and the sync() is called on every record. We could disable the thread and not have it flush every n secs unnecessarily.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
